- Use logistics terms precisely: 3PL/WMS/Incoterms/HS/berth/DEM-DET/stowage.
- Default risk triggers (guideline):
  - ΔRate > 10.00% → cost overrun risk
  - ETA delay > 24.00h → OTIF risk
  - Deck pressure > 4.00 t/m² → stowage risk
  - Cert expiry < 30d → compliance risk (MOIAT/FANR human gate)
